{%- comment -%}
  ============================================
  SEO Schema Markup - JSON-LD Structured Data
  ============================================
  This snippet outputs appropriate schema.org structured data
  based on the current page type. Include in theme.liquid <head>.

  Covers:
  - Organization/WebSite (all pages)
  - CollectionPage + ItemList (collection pages)
  - BreadcrumbList (collection & product pages)
  - Product with aggregateRating (product pages - handled in product-information.liquid)
  - FAQPage (pages with FAQ sections)

  @author Xinzuo SEO Implementation
{%- endcomment -%}

